{
  "stem": "13911.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they knew about these partisans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they threw a few bombs in that village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we immediately knew that, hey, that's no good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Run in the woods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we ran deep into the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we begged for some bread, because a lot of the farmers, of the peasants, ran into the woods, too, with the cattle and the horses, because they knew they were going to bomb and destroy everything.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the Germans came again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we knew-- they were circling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- we could hear the-- the planes above our heads, like bees, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And like the Jews, the group of Jews, said, he'll stay-- staying here is just senseless.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have to take a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And started walking out the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Also, we met a Russian dispatcher in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, it was very close to the front line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were-- we could hear the artillery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was the front line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they-- there was a dispatcher to help, to see, partisans, or whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told us that-- where the Russians are stationed now, where they are now, at what point.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he says, the only way for you to try and survive is to start running toward the-- the Russian side, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We divided-- the Jews-- the Poles stayed on there, and then, sure-- soon enough, the planes came and leveled everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But again, [LAUGHS] we got out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Did this partisan group have weapons and try to do any sabotage, or--?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [INAUDIBLE] rifles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I-- I don't even know, because we weren't part of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't-- they let us hang around, because they had better things to do, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
